long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: An innovative community supervision tool designed to assist clients and their families in getting out the starting blocks and into an action phase. It was designed to help them reach major milestones in their quest to live productive, law-abiding and enriched lives following entanglement with the criminal justice system.
